my mother was a Baptist - a Methodist, Baptist Methodist. And it wasn't until about 1910 or '11 when she changed over to the church. Church of England. Up to me being about eleven years of age and then she changed over to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Church{\*\xmlclose} of {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}England.{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}; And that was St Pauls church, Carlton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4466232 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14110736\charrsid21882 How often would she go to church?
