No. But my mother used to do a tremendous amount of work for the church, such things as - cleaning the bras
ses and - altar linens and all these sort of things and arranging the flowers at weekends and - and - even washing surplices for the choirboys and - getting 'em up you know. She was a tremendous church worker. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4466232 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14110736\charrsid21882 And you were in the Scouts attached to the church?
