No. No. You were paid - according to - how many telegrams you took out. Oh yes. Used to get three for things a telegram in those days. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4466232 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14110736\charrsid21882 You weren't paid a fixed wage them?
